      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is ready for some TLC and offers a great opportunity for someone looking to put in a little work! While it needs some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a solid starting point for a fixer-upper or a simple neighborhood runabout.",
