    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience for the next owner. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, there are no major mechanical issues or significant damage. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for daily use and has many miles left to give.",
