    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is currently non-operational. The engine requires a complete rebuild or replacement, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping when it was last running. Cosmetically, the car has extensive rust along the frame and wheel wells, along with several large dents and a cracked windshield. The interior has sustained significant wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is an ideal candidate for a parts car or a very ambitious restoration project for someone with the necessary mechanical expertise.",
      "price": 3500.0,
